name: BizAuto
description: BizAuto is a cryptoasset that can be used as a means of payment and BizAuto MainNet improves transaction speed and applies quantum random number technology to enhance security by adopting a consensus algorithm of the Delegated Proof-of-Stake (DPoS). New internet service must be built under this premise of Web 3.0 in line with this great transition, and BizAuto project develops a system for the Web 3.0 Internet service and provides various tools to ultimately create a new business ecosystem suitable for the Web 3.0 era.
